T.query: select e.emp_no  as emp_no ,s.salary,e.first_name,e.last_name,e.birth_date,e.hire_date,s.from_date,d.dept_no from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date join dept_emp de on de.emp_no = e.emp_no join departments d on de.dept_no = d.dept_no where (e.emp_no > 50000 and t.from_date > '1990-01-01' and de.from_date > '1990-01-01' and e.last_name like 'A%' and d.dept_no !='d002' and s.salary > 50000 ) or (  t.title like '%Engineer%' and e.birth_date > '1965-01-01' and s.to_date > '2000-01-01') or t.to_date = '1997-01-01';

F.query: select e.emp_no  as emp_no ,s.salary,e.first_name,e.last_name,e.birth_date,e.hire_date,s.from_date,d.dept_no from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date join dept_emp de on de.emp_no = e.emp_no join departments d on de.dept_no = d.dept_no where (e.emp_no > 50000 and t.from_date > '1992-01-01' and de.from_date > '1992-01-01' and e.first_name like 'A%' and d.dept_no !='d002' and s.salary > 45000 ) or ( t.title like '%Engineer%' and e.birth_date > '1965-01-01' ) or t.to_date = '1998-01-01';
